  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself \u2014 the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Uncertainty quantification was performed across material property and geometric tolerance distributions; a screening sensitivity study was conducted verbally as part of the UQ narrative to identify dominant contributors, though no structured sensitivity analysis object is linked.",
